<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4550180>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 12. (a, b) Clathrocaspia pallasii (Clessin & Dybowski in Dybowski, 1887), paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 104). (c, d) C. pallasii, lectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 104). (e) C. pallasii, paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 105). (f) C. pallasii, specimen labelled as “Caspia microcingulifera, paratype”, locality 9 (ZIN, no number). (g, h) C. pallasii, paratype of C. isseli (Logvinenko & Starobogatov, 1969), locality 14 (ZIN, no number). (i, j). C. isseli, paratype, locality 21 (ZIN, no number). (k) C. isseli, specimen misidentified as C. pallasii, locality 16 (ZIN, no number). (l, q) C. isseli, from Holocene deposits of the Kura delta (locality 25f, RGM 1310305). (m, n) C. pallasii, paratype of Pyrgula sowinskyi, locality 24 (ZIN, no number). (o, r) C. pallasii, paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 105). (p, s) C. pallasii, paralectotype, locality 26 (ZB-M W.Dyb. 74). Scale bars = 1 mm (a–n), 100 μm (o–s)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4550180/files/figure.png" .

